Rating: 4
This one rocks! I love corn soup and I've made every recipe I can find including Ina Garten's and this is a fantastic version. It's simple to make, especially if you have an immersion blender. I was apprehensive about the clam sauce and the ginger, but what's interesting is that you don't taste them in this recipe. The onion, ginger and clam sauce all blend together to create this magnificent flavor. I used backfin crab (that's all they had). If you don't want to make the crab part, just make the soup. It's awesome all on its own.

